Sign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015599, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Him the Master who took my hand and saved me from the disastrous situations! He wiped off my wrongdoings and took care of my important needs. He made us needless of the creatures and did not let my provisions be in the hands of those who are themselves provided for. He made me reputable in the world, and recorded my name amongst those who are mentioned. He did not make me suffer from haughtiness that would lower my rank, and did not make me suffer from the darkness of His Wrath and Chastisements!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "SUBHAA-NAHU SAIYYEDAN A-KHAZA BE-YADEE MINAL WARA-TAATE WA MAH-HASA A’NNIL KHATEE-ATE WA KAFAA-NIL MOHIM-MAATE WA AGH-NAA NEE A’NIL MAKH-LOO-QEENA WA LAM YAJ-A’L RIZQEE ILAL MARZOO-QEENA WA SHAHARA ZIKREE FIL A’A-LAMEENA WA JA-A’LAS MEE FIL MAZKOO-REENA WA LAM YUSH-QENEE BE-U’J-BIN.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَهٗ سَيِّدًا اَخَذَ بِيَدِيْ مِنَ الْوَرَطَاتِ وَمَحَّصَ عَنِّي الْخَطِيْئَاتِ وَكَفَانِي الْمُهِمَّاتِ وَاَغْنَانِيْ عَنِ الْمَخْلُوْقِيْنَ وَلَمْ يَجْعَلْ رِزْقِيْ اِلَى الْمَرْزُوْقِيْنَ‌ وَشَهَرَ ذِكْرِيْ فِي الْعَالَمِيْنَ وَجَعَلَ اسْمِيْ فِي الْمَذْكُوْرِيْنَ وَلَمْ يُشْقِنِيْ بِعُجْبٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "Ara