RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "He did not make me suffer from considering what is forbidden to be legitimate that could strip off the robes of His Mercy from me and wear the robes of His Wrath instead! I thank Him alone and I worship Him only! I have hopes of increase and perfection from Him! There is no change nor any strength except by God the Sublime, the Supreme and may God bestow blessings on the Prophet Muhammad (s.a.w.a) and his Progeny (a.s) and may His peace be on them plentifully.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "YA-HUTTO-NEE A’N DARA-JAATIN RAFEE-A’TIN FA-YOHWEE BEE ILAA ZOLAME GHAZA-BEHI WA NIQ-MATE-HI WA LAA ABLAA-NEE BISTEH-LAALIN YANZE-O’ A’NNEE MALAA-BESA RAHMATE-HI WA YO-A’WWE-ZONEE LE-BO-SIZ-ZOLLE MIN SA-KHATE-HI IYYAA-HO ASH-KORO WA LAHU A’BODO WA MINHO ARJUT TA-MAAMA WAL-MAZEEDA WA LAA HAWLA WA LAA QUWWATA ILLAA BILLAA-HIL A’LIYYIL A’ZEEME WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN NABIYYE WA AALE-HI WA SALLAMA TASLEE-MAN.", "ArabicText1": "يَحُطُّنِيْ عَنْ دَرَجَاتٍ رَفِيْعَةٍ فَيُهْوِيْ بِيْ اِلٰى ظُلَمِ غَضَبِهٖ وَنِقْمَتِهٖ وَلَا اَبْلَانِيْ بِاسْتِحْلَالٍ يَنْزِعُ عَنِّيْ مَلَابِسَ رَحْمَتِهٖ وَيُعَوِّضُنِيْ لِبُؤْسِ الذُّلِّ مِنْ سَخَطِهٖ اِيَّاهُ اَشْكُرُ وَلَهٗ اَعْبُدُ وَمِنْهُ اَرْجُو التَّمَامَ وَ الْمَزِيْدَ وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ اِلَّا بِاللهِ الْعَلِيِّ الْعَظِيْمِ وَصَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ النَّبِيِّ وَآلِهٖ وَسَلَّمَ تَسْلِيْمًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicR